name: Stinky - Neon Socks
description:
These are the Neon Socks. These are the sickest Snowboard socks in the game.  Right and Left Specific toes shape Comfort band, shock absorption cushion area, Elastic arch support, padded toe, reinforced heel, cushioned arch for extra comfort!

30%Cotton, 42% PYP-Prolen, 21%Nylon, 2% Elastan. 
AEGIS Antibacterial protection (So they don't stink!) Cool cotton max fast moisture absorption (keep your feet from being wet!)

For ages socks were not supposed to be seen. They were neglected hard – they were hidden under long leggings, inside new shoes or colored in gray, unattractive colors. But not anymore. Meet Stinky! These are socks that know how to behave in public – they are bold, colorful, and the only stinky about them is their name.

Sizing for L/XL is 
Size 10-13 (mens) 
Size 11-15(womens)

S/M is 
Size 5-10 (mens) 
Size 7-10 (womens)

xs/s is
Size 5 and under (Mens)
Size 7 and under (womens)

Pack design done by Slav Vitanov
http://slavnoev.tumblr.com/
